name: GBOY
description: About G*BOY At the heart of our ecosystem is $GBOY, one of the first AI-native IP tokens - a hooded destroyer symbolizing rebellion, freedom, and chaos. As a memecoin launch vehicle for NEUKO, $GBOY drives attention and revenue by leveraging proprietary AI infrastructure, a viral meme collection, and an evangelistic community ready to capture mindshare in uncertain markets. In six weeks G*BOY has garnered millions of views, surpassed all major NFTs and memecoins in marketshare for extended periods during the campaign, and was recently voted as a finalist for most viral X campaign at the Solana Community Spotlight awards.
